text:
Snyder Avenue, no. 35
Flatbush Town Hall, erected 1875.

View 1 (horizontal):
Flatbush Town Hall in 1877. Brainard Collection, Brooklyn Museum. (now at Bklyn Pub. Lib.)

View 2 (vertical):
Same building, 1971. Presently headquarters of the 67th Precinct, N. Y. Police Department.
Photographer: Irving Choban

Photostat Wey #A-1414
